headline: Labcorp Holdings (NYSE:LH) Expands Precision Oncology Portfolio with FDA-Authorized Liquid Biopsy Tests
summary: Labcorp Holdings (NYSE:LH) announced an expansion of its precision oncology portfolio with two new solutions, Labcorp Plasma Detect and PGDx elio Plasma Focus Dx, aimed at improving patient care in oncology. These developments, along with upcoming presentations at the AACR 2025 Annual Meeting, align with the company's ongoing efforts to innovate in the medical field.
